body:
An interesting case for when there are many test positions per file.

Perhaps, a non-static factory in `FileSource` would also work?

```java
	public FileSource withPosition(FilePosition position) {
		Preconditions.notNull(position, "position must not be null");
		return direct(file, position); // new FileSource without canonicalPath call
	}
```

I just spiked it.

```java
private FileSource(FileSource fileSource, FilePosition filePosition) {
	this.file = fileSource.file;
	this.filePosition = filePosition;
}

public FileSource withPosition(FilePosition filePosition) {
	Preconditions.notNull(filePosition, "filePosition must not be null");
	return new FileSource(this, filePosition);
}
```
